@startuml svc-inventory-procurement--post-purchase-orders

!include ../theme.puml
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #0891b2
}

header [[/microservices/svc-inventory-procurement/#integration-context ⬆ svc-inventory-procurement Integration Context]]

title POST /purchase-orders\nCreate purchase order\n<size:10><color:#7c3aed>ARCHITECT OVERRIDE — enriched with supplier workflow and payment gate</color></size>

participant "Client" as Client [[/applications/]]
participant "API Gateway" as GW [[/actors/#api-gateway]] #E0F2FE
participant "svc-inventory-procurement" as Svc [[/microservices/svc-inventory-procurement/]] #F1F5F9
participant "Gear Inventory" as GI [[/microservices/svc-gear-inventory/]] #CFFAFE
participant "Supplier Portal" as Supplier #F3E8FF
participant "Payments Svc" as Pay [[/microservices/svc-payments/]] #F1F5F9
participant "Notifications" as Ntfy [[/microservices/svc-notifications/]] #F1F5F9
database "PostgreSQL" as DB [[/microservices/svc-inventory-procurement/#data-store]] #FEF9C3

note over Svc
  [[/services/api/svc-inventory-procurement.html View in Swagger UI]]
end note

Client -> GW : POST /purchase-orders
activate GW #0891b2
GW -> Svc : route request
activate Svc #0891b2

note right of Svc : Validate PO request\n(items, quantities, supplier_id)\nCheck requester authorization

== Verify Item Catalog ==

Svc -> GI : [[/microservices/svc-gear-inventory/#get-gear-items-list-gear-inventory GET /gear-items]]
activate GI #CFFAFE
GI --> Svc : Gear catalog\n(item details, current stock,\nreorder thresholds)
deactivate GI

note right of Svc : Validate all items exist\nin gear catalog\nCheck reorder justification:\nstock < reorder_threshold?

== Supplier Submission ==

Svc -> Supplier : Submit purchase order\n(items, quantities, delivery_date,\nshipping_address)
activate Supplier #F3E8FF
alt Supplier accepts order
    Supplier --> Svc : PO accepted\n(supplier_po_number, estimated_delivery)
    deactivate Supplier
else Supplier rejects (item discontinued, etc.)
    Supplier --> Svc : PO rejected\n(rejection_reason, affected_items)
    deactivate Supplier
    note right of Svc #FEE2E2 : Mark PO as REJECTED\nNotify procurement team
    Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO purchase_orders\n(status = REJECTED, reason)
    activate DB #FEF9C3
    DB --> Svc : Created
    deactivate DB
    Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Notify procurement team]]
    Svc --> GW : 422 Unprocessable\n(rejection_reason)
    deactivate Svc
    GW --> Client : 422 Unprocessable
    deactivate GW
end

== Process PO Payment ==

Svc -[#DC2626]> Pay : [[/microservices/svc-payments/#post-payments-process-a-payment POST /payments]]\n(type = PURCHASE_ORDER,\namount = po_total,\npayee = supplier_account)
activate Pay #F1F5F9
Pay --> Svc : Payment processed\n(payment_id)
deactivate Pay

== Record Purchase Order ==

Svc -> DB : INSERT INTO purchase_orders\n(po_id, supplier_id, items,\ntotal_amount, payment_id,\nsupplier_po_number,\nstatus = APPROVED)
activate DB #FEF9C3
DB --> Svc : Created row
deactivate DB

== Async Notification ==

Svc ->> Ntfy : [[/microservices/svc-notifications/#post-notifications-send-a-notification Notify procurement team]]

Svc --> GW : 201 Created\n(po_id, supplier_po_number,\nestimated_delivery, status)
deactivate Svc
GW --> Client : 201 Created
deactivate GW

@enduml
